---
import planksImg from "../images/planks.jpg";

const planksImgUrl = `url(${planksImg.src})`;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Text Effects</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>5 fun<span>(and easy)</span><br /> css effects</h1>
      <div>
        Lorem, ipsum dolor sit
        <a href="#" class="fancy">
          amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Expedita perferendis distinctio
          quos! Deleniti aperiam ad, atque magni, excepturi
        </a>
        facere voluptatem neque doloribus laudantium dolor commodi? Excepturi nemo
        modi quasi magnam.
      </div>
      <hr />
      <div>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit, <a href="#" class="fancy">amet consectetur</a> adipisicing
        elit. Asperiores labore fugit quasi nulla in facere, quos exercitationem
        repellendus! Autem animi deleniti voluptates ipsa nesciunt est soluta quaerat
        ullam ipsam dolor.
      </div>

      <h2 class="image">Image text example</h2>
      <div>
        Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Voluptas ex
        aut obcaecati sunt. Obcaecati, repudiandae! Veritatis eum, laborum iure
        cumque ad reiciendis accusamus ex corrupti omnis quam eveniet ut
        maiores?.
      </div>

      <h2 class="gradient">Image text example</h2>
      <div>
        Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Voluptates
        minus nostrum voluptatum corporis rem doloremque. Enim numquam
        accusantium error. Ad perferendis error esse sapiente eos ducimus ex
        quos quo praesentium.
